## 1. Folder Structure

Every challenge lives in its own folder. The name should be a descriptive slug in lowercase with hyphens and no spaces.

```
challenge-name/
    DATASET.md
    PROBLEM.md
    RUBRICS.md
    generate_dataset.py
    prepare.py
    grade.py
    run_solution.py
    solution.py
    solution.ipynb
    dataset/
        raw_data_file.csv
        public/
